<p>The conversion rate is the percentage of visitors who take a desired action—such as making a purchase. Purchase could be something that someone wants to buy on your ecommerce site. It is determined by the number of goals (conversions) reached divided by the total amount of visitors and then multiplied by 100.</p>

<pre>
