          <p>The B2B funnel strategy used by Tank Retailer demonstrates the value of tuning specialized funnels to specific market segments. Their government and commercial customers type of business demanded a radically different approach than what we are all used to — content marketing, education materials, consultative selling, relationship nurturing with long sales cycles.</p>
          
